{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/Crash.gif?t=1730053811\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> You are the sole survivor of a devastating spaceship crash, stranded on a frozen, desolate planet. Now, you must scavenge whatever scraps remain in a desperate attempt to call for help.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Remote-Controlled Exploration</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/ROBOT.gif?t=1730053811\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Trapped within the hollow shell of your ship, deploy a scrap recovery bot to venture into the outside world. Search for what scarce resources this planet offers and uncover the mystery behind your crash.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">An Unfolding Landscape</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/PipeBurst2.gif?t=1730053811\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Severe weather conditions constantly reshape the world around you, revealing new areas along with what lies dormant beneath.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A Mystery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/journal_crop.png?t=1730053811\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On this planet full of secrets, it's up to you to piece together the puzzle. Use your journal to document your findings and uncover the truth before it\u2019s too late.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A Slow Descent into Madness</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/MONSTER.gif?t=1730053811\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The cold makes sleep elusive, blurring the line between reality and paranoia. Whatev